ghting Service.</li>\r\n	<li><strong class=\"uppercase\"><a href=\"http://gigazonegaming.local/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Rate-OP-Controlled-Electric-Heat-and-Water-Heating-10-11.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\">Rate Schedule “OP” </a></strong> Off Peak Electric Heat and Water Heating</li>\r\n</ul>','General Service Retail Rates','','publish','open','open','','general-service-retail-rates','','','2016-03-01 20:06:12','2016-03-01 20:06:12','',94,'http://gigazonegaming.local/auto-draft/',0,'post','',0),
